snippet.title: This is Create. (2022)
snippet.description:
It was due time to revisit our Cake assembly line for a few touch ups!

Create is a powerful Minecraft mod nearing three years of Development. It adds a variety of useful building tools, as well as technology based on kinetics and rotational power. It is a free-time open-source project by a bunch of Minecraft players who love the creative aspect of the game.

Project Page
Curseforge: https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/create
Modrinth: https://modrinth.com/mod/create

- Join the Supporters:  https://www.patreon.com/simibubi
- Tell us your Feedback and Ideas: https://discord.gg/hmaD7Se
- Watch more Videos: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCrKV2QTuyGcv4E3eSJpBiYA/playlists

Mods present during recording:
Create, Flywheel, Optifine, Minema Resurrected

Please note: This video is recorded in-game footage, However: 
At the moment, using Shaders with Create in scenes this complex will not usually render at playable frame rates. For the purposes of this showcase, the game engine was slowed down in order to create a smooth looking recording.

Shaderpack: Complementary Reimagined
Map by: Kryppers, D'Arcy Olla, evanthebruce, Zelophed, dani, simibubi, vectorwing, Grimmauld
Get the save file here: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ldD2WMXFUaiO3hqaW0s-Mmp0IcuQD7TI/view?usp=sharing

Music choice and timing: LeastReality
Video recorded and edited by: Kryppers
Music: Waltz of the Flowers by Tchaikovsky (from YouTube Studio)

Thank you for watching and have fun with Create!
